thread.title: Tanya Chandler
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Tanya Chandler

author: Tanya Chandler
title: Tanya Chandler
text: We hired a vehicle in Auckland and travelled through the North Island. Ace were wonderful do deal with, we would recommend them to anyone. Value for money and they also collect and drop you back to meet your flights at the Airport.
